{"title":"观大剧院舞","authors":["袁水拍　叶浅予"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":10,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"观大剧院舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍　诗  叶浅予　速写"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌兰诺娃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绣幕开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天鹅飞来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湛蓝的海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足尖儿点水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亭亭一枝莲花白。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪一般单纯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰一般坚贞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云一般轻盈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦一般恬静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜜也似的爱情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳边轻送，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句话儿知心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从远方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带给六亿人民……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“斯大林格勒人”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满台融融战火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年伏尔加河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢盔碎，军衣破，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目眦裂，气吞魔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人倒下去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百人冲向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫国卫主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢铁意志坚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场强烈的舞蹈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座不朽的雕像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面不倒的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万人心上飘扬！（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上图：乌兰诺娃的“天鹅之死”下图和右图：列皮辛斯卡娅和谢尔盖耶夫在双人舞中（选自歌剧“唐·吉诃德”）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}